{"id":332047,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2014/02/记者刘虎案北京市公安局起诉意见书/","date":"2014-02-02T22:59:36Z","modified":"2015-09-10T09:53:21Z","title":"记者刘虎案北京市公安局起诉意见书","content":"<p>来源：作者微博（<a href=\"http://weibo.com/u/1684232061\">@记者刘向南</a>）</p>\n<blockquote><p>@周泽律师：【用心良苦】罪记者,必杀技是毁其道义形象。如,揭其受贿或敲诈以谋私利,记者道义形象立毁。于是,公权便可上下其手。刘虎案,公安先以寻衅滋事拘,继以寻衅滋事、诽谤报捕;检察院以诽谤批捕,公安复以诽谤移送起诉;遭退卷后继以寻衅滋事、敲诈勒索、诽谤三罪换一检察院移送!然,让求删微博者助残,敲诈乎?</p>\n<p>@周泽律师：公安人员在讯问中给刘虎提供了两个榜样,一个是魏巍,写了《谁是最可爱的人》;一个是穆青,写了《记党的好干部焦裕录》,说刘虎十几年记者生涯中&#8221;也曾为公共利益做了很报道和努力&#8221;,但把网民提供的、未经查证的信息通过微博发布,&#8221;使党的形象受到了损害&#8221;,让其反思发帖的思想根源。</p></blockquote>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2014/02/6463577djw1ed4xqvpypgj20hs0nsgp0.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-332048\" alt=\"6463577djw1ed4xqvpypgj20hs0nsgp0\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2014/02/6463577djw1ed4xqvpypgj20hs0nsgp0.jpg\" width=\"512\" height=\"685\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2014/02/6463577djw1ed4xqvpypgj20hs0nsgp0.jpg 640w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2014/02/6463577djw1ed4xqvpypgj20hs0nsgp0-224x300.jpg 224w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 512px) 100vw, 512px\" /></a> <a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2014/02/6463577djw1ed4xqyv2ewj20hs0nsgo6.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-332049\" alt=\"6463577djw1ed4xqyv2ewj20hs0nsgo6\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2014/02/6463577djw1ed4xqyv2ewj20hs0nsgo6.jpg\" width=\"512\" height=\"685\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2014/02/6463577djw1ed4xqyv2ewj20hs0nsgo6.jpg 640w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2014/02/6463577djw1ed4xqyv2ewj20hs0nsgo6-224x300.jpg 224w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 512px) 100vw, 512px\" /></a></p>\n","author":980,"categories":[18271,18270,18269,9203],"tags":[23782,23669,11544,9006]}